title: The Path Afterlife 2009 x264 aac MP4
description:
The Path documentary has filmed 13 individuals who are well versed, knowledgeable and currently practicing, studying or are experts in the field of holistic studies, out of body experiences, reiki, past life regression, physics and integrative medicine. Well renowned authors, practitioners and well respected local practitioners in Upstate New York will give their expertise on their own souls path, what they have learned along the way and their knowledge about the afterlife. The captured interviews of all participants will also examine ways in which one can heal themselves and compare the differences and commonalities of Eastern and Western Medicine.

The stories and accounts of each practitioner's experiences, education and studies on this subject will lead the audience into the direction of being able to make a more educated decision about Eastern philosophies and how these topics relate to their lives. The projects theme in all DVDs will focus on healing the spirit and soul. The DVD series will be targeted to the mainstream audience in order to educate people to consider alterative practices to achieve optimal health and overall a higher quality of living in this lifetime on this planet.

It is the hope that this documentary will eliminate some of the fear associated with death and answer more questions about spiritual realms in order to allow people the freedom to make their own informed decision about life after death with the new knowledge they learn from The Path documentary.
